name: Wrapped MoonCats (MCAT20)
description:
MoonCats are procedurally generated pixel cats which are deterministically generated based on blockchain data. They're the oldest known Ethereum asset to use generative creation, which allowed anyone to locate and rescue MoonCats. 25,440 MoonCats have now been rescued from the moon, and now you can be a part of the next chapter of their lives!

This token represents fractional ownership of a MoonCat in the NFT20 pool. 100 MCAT20 tokens can be exchanged for any MoonCat from the pool.
